It serves health and aged care, community, education, finance and corporate services, tech and IT, trades and labour, agriculture and food processing, and defence sectors. The company was formerly known as People Infrastructure Ltd and changed its name to Peoplein Limited in December 2021. Peoplein Limited was founded in 1996 and is based in Fortitude Valley, Australia.
